window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Level Up. Kill Everyone Else. Take Their Stuff. </p> <p>All Dantem ever wanted was one teeny tiny, almost insignificant thing....</p> <p>Vengeance on those who wronged him. </p> <p>When he’s suddenly recruited by the world’s largest video game company, he will finally have a way to achieve his dream. </p> <p>Assuming, of course, he has no problem being the bad guy.</p>"; 
